{"tid":2033610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我支持bno平權，但。。。","createTime":"2020-05-24T18:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T11:58:54.000Z","uid":270276,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41da89a49c2078cfec87e150c1ad76399a5ed1cf","tid":2033610,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:15:18.000Z","msg":"但我希望係97前既比番居英權(即使無申請過bno)，97後既以難民身份比居英權，以上既必需證明無違反人權自由<br />\n<br />\n當然未到最後關頭都唔走，但被迫走既時候救得一個得一個。<br />\n<br />\n利申有bno"},{"pid":"948951652e7b560c9704fed1f5ec57bbd08ab69f","tid":2033610,"uid":118112,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41da89a49c2078cfec87e150c1ad76399a5ed1cf","tid":2033610,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:15:18.000Z","msg":"但我希望係97前既比番居英權(即使無申請過bno)，97後既以難民身份比居英權，以上既必需證明無違反人權自由<br />\n<br />\n當然未到最後關頭都唔走，但被迫走既時候救得一個得一個。<br />\n<br />\n利申有bno"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔可以留底97後既手足<br />\n要走一齊走"},{"pid":"8c9ad8b76f09eaee78e4370e6d42ece73b56f1c4","tid":2033610,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"bno既話題，希望唔好再講下去，因為好多更緊要既野必需做。"},{"pid":"a16447d1d8e19b0dedbdfee71fe8b6214c45eb59","tid":2033610,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"19eb0c24c3c87d2c51b0f3691282fc51de212e35","tid":2033610,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T19:42:47.000Z","msg":"個個諗撚住走 咁反乜鳩國安法?"},{"pid":"b7c9df31e01c0e66c3b86d0f768903aeea2087e2","tid":2033610,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19eb0c24c3c87d2c51b0f3691282fc51de212e35","tid":2033610,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T19:42:47.000Z","msg":"個個諗撚住走 咁反乜鳩國安法?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:06:45.000Z","msg":"而家只係吹可能比居英權。。。我唔抱信心。<br />\n<br />\n搞好而家既戰線先。習大攬炒我地，佢博緊世界為錢唔會真搞中國，所以要加強國際線條路，吸多d外國支持者，我地又要減少被拉風險。"},{"pid":"11a881ab75864068f4432895e440ec52bf8a874e","tid":2033610,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DWe6lGKgH4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDWe6lGKgH4M&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=9114837e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DWe6lGKgH4M</a>"},{"pid":"f0980f1e4d6a4e126b8a5bfc790106db0cf8fe80","tid":2033610,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"189e01d4bb8f59a8d89e1bc6959a270d41af8c6a","tid":2033610,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ep_xAvPu-Ik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEp_xAvPu-Ik&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=67551892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ep_xAvPu-Ik</a>"},{"pid":"8ed9ad0b8aca47f7878b7bd53b180b706a922021","tid":2033610,"uid":270276,